---
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        What is <span class="text-primary">Stride</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Stride is one of those words that looks simple but carries a surprising amount of motion packed into six letters.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        At its core, <strong>stride</strong> means: <em>A long, confident step forward.</em> It implies purpose. You're not shuffling or wandering—you're moving with direction and intention. In a figurative sense, it also means making progress or advancing toward a goal.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- STRIDE Acronym -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-secondary/5 to-accent/5 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          <span class="text-primary">S</span> <span class="text-secondary">T</span> <span class="text-primary">R</span> <span class="text-secondary">I</span> <span class="text-primary">D</span> <span class="text-secondary">E</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 font-semibold">
          Smart Travel Routes & Insights for Discovery and Experience
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        
        <!-- S - Smart -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">S</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Smart</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Because the system isn't just a map; it's an intelligent local guide powered by AI.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- T - Travel -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary">T</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Travel</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Captures movement, commuting, exploring—whether it's jeepneys, shops, cafés, or routes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- R - Routes -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">R</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Routes</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                The heart of the app: finding paths, directions, and nearest terminals.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- I - Insights -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary">I</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Insights</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                The system doesn't just tell where, it provides helpful context, options, and local knowledge.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- D - Discovery -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">D</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Discovery</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                For uncovering new local spots—restaurants, shops, landmarks—beyond the usual tourist stops.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- E - Experience -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary">E</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Experience</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                The whole journey becomes smoother, richer, and more enjoyable.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

